{"tid":973945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德極右派議員被打重傷 各政黨譴責暴力","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T15:07:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"364da3a17096d2eaad3215362f4da058a09ead10","tid":973945,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/01/08/b6d5bca14b7032456b5ff963da9eecb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Fb6d5bca14b7032456b5ff963da9eecb0.jpg&h=5814610d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國的反移民民粹政黨、德國另類選擇黨(AfD)的不來梅支部代表麥格尼茲，7日下午在市中心遭到襲擊。(圖：AfD臉書)<br />\n<br />\n德國警方今天(8日)表示，1名極右派國會議員在德國北部一起「出於政治動機」的群眾襲擊事件中受到重傷。<br />\n<br />\n德國的反移民民粹政黨、德國另類選擇黨(AfD)的不來梅(Bremen)支部代表麥格尼茲(Frank Magnitz)，7日下午在市中心遭到襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，「依據受害者的工作研判，我們相信這是出於政治動機的舉動」。<br />\n<br />\nAfD黨公佈一張麥格尼茲躺在醫院病床上意識不清的照片，他臉上流著血、臉部腫脹，前額還留有一道深痕傷口。<br />\n<br />\n據說有3名蒙面歹徒進行襲擊行動。<br />\n<br />\n該黨在一份聲明中表示，「他們持木棍將他打到失去意識後，然後在地上踢他」，並補充指出，有1名建築工人曾介入阻止這場襲擊。<br />\n<br />\nAfD黨表示：「今天是德國民主黑暗的一天」。<br />\n<br />\nAfD黨主席默爾騰(Joerg Meuthen)在推特上表示，麥格尼茲在一場「懦弱且令人憤怒」的襲擊中「幾乎快要被打死」。<br />\n<br />\n執政聯盟中的社民黨(Social Democrats)國會議員卡爾斯(Johannes Kahrs)說，「永遠不能接受暴力」，以及「任何形式的極端主義都是垃圾」。他祝福麥格尼茲早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n反對派綠黨(Greens party)的歐德米(Cem Ozdemir)表示，他希望嫌犯能「儘速被繩之以法」，以及，即使反對極右派政黨，「也沒有任何理由能讓暴力正當化」。<br />\n<br />\n這位土耳其裔的政治人物說，「那些以仇恨來打擊仇恨的人，最終只是讓仇恨獲勝」。<br />\n<br />\n上週，一枚放在垃圾箱裡的爆裂裝置爆炸，造成AfD薩克森州(Saxony)黨部辦公室嚴重毀損，3名嫌犯遭到逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n此外，上週AfD黨下薩克森州(Lower Saxony)1名政治人物的住家遭到塗鴉，當地黨部辦公室也遭到漆彈攻擊。<br />\n<br />\nAfD黨在2017年9月的大選中，以近13％的選票進入德國國會，成為下議院中勢力最大的反對黨。<br />\n<br />\n外界預料AfD黨在今年5月的歐洲大選，以及今年稍後在前東德地區的三次地方選舉中，將有更多斬獲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2007625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2007625&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPzuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=7eca8456\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2007625</a>"},{"pid":"ffef3e6fe70a561198251cc01edc8526d27f64ab","tid":973945,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"極左極右一家親"},{"pid":"6aed8d307725e55f936dbea50493d55bbadee328","tid":973945,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"Punch the nazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fded5ca3678dffac0e7714de585f1bf21535eaa","tid":973945,"uid":52946,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"德國自己攞黎賤怪邊個"},{"pid":"e003879bb6570c7fef5f9f18a0407bd46ea1c43c","tid":973945,"uid":36775,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"極右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明係愛國組織"},{"pid":"f84478978972070f367ca9e01883b97c91a3339d","tid":973945,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次輪到邊個"},{"pid":"3579cd95f7cc1b8b1c97c88605e256b8f41b3443","tid":973945,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"好包容好理性"},{"pid":"c8d3a2a424ea907ff5f804336f07afc7c186628c","tid":973945,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aed8d307725e55f936dbea50493d55bbadee328","tid":973945,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"Punch the nazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"